counterpart David Levy.
</P>
<P>
Qian is on the third leg of his current Middle East tour, which
will also take him to Palestinian-rule area and Egypt. He is
scheduled to meet Palestinian National Authority President Yasser
Arafat and other officials in Gaza Tuesday. 
