<HEADLINE> China Says It Will Improve Technical Supervision </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 23 (Xinhua) -- The director of the State
Administration for Technical Supervision, Li Chuanqing, said today
that improving efficiancy will be the main goal of next year's
technical supervision work.
</P>
<P>
Technical supervision should focus on improving the quality of
products, straightening up the market, and improving basic
techniques, Li told a national conference on technical
supervision, which opened in Beijing today.
</P>
<P>
