should also pay attention to self-improvement, and have reforms to
improve their service.
</P>
<P>
Technical supervision should also meet the needs of reforms in
state-run enterprises, the market system, technical standards of
township enterprises, and of introducing international standards
for technical supervision, Li noted. 
