<HEADLINE> North China Province to Promote Tourism in 1998 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 23 (Xinhua) -- North China's Shanxi Province
will focus on eight tour itineraries and three festivals in
1998, according to officials attending a recent tourism promotion
campaign in Beijing.
</P>
<P>
