province's travel attractions, including the Yungang Grottos in
Datong City, the Huayan Temple, the famous wooden tower in
Yingxian County, the temples in the Wutai Mountain, the ancient
city of Pingyao, the Yongle Palace in Ruicheng County, the Hukou
Waterfall on the Yellow River and many other scenic spots.
</P>
<P>
The province, the birthplace of the Chinese nation, has a long
history filled with numerous folk features. In addition, Shanxi
leads all the Chinese provinces in terms of ancient buildings,
according to an official.
</P>
<P>
Shanxi's tourism agencies will organize various travel programs
featuring traditional and religious culture, historical
events, ancient architecture, the scenery along the Yellow River,
folk customs, ancient ruins and rural areas.
</P>
<P>
The three tourism festivals will be offered between July and
October. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
