He estimated that the turnover of the firms will rise by 20
percent on last year's figure of 122.1 billion yuan.
</P>
<P>
The official said that more than 90 multinational companies,
including 25 of the world's top 100 companies, have undertaken
projects in the coastal province.
</P>
<P>
He noted that foreign investors are showing a great interest
in investing in the province's infrastructure and energy projects.
</P>
<P>
In 1996, the province approved a 600 million US dollar project
for the power industry, and recently approved a similiar
project which will involve a total investment of 2.2 billion
US dollars.
