<HEADLINE> Ukrainian Airliner's Black Box Found </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KIEV, December 22 (Xinhua) -- The black box flight recorder
from the crashed Ukrainian Yak-42 airliner has been found, the
Ukrainian Ministry of Emergency Affairs said Sunday.
</P>
<P>
