<TEXT>
<P>
BRASILIA, December 22 (Xinhua) -- Brazilian aeronautical
company Embraer and U.S. Amr Eagle Inc. signed a contract for the
manufacturing and exportation of 67 ERJ-145 jets for commercial
use, the president of a Brazilian bank said Monday.
</P>
